      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable friend. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it runs beautifully and looks great both inside and out. It\u2019s perfect for anyone who wants a dependable, comfy ride without any fuss. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love driving it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 33800.0,
