    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant. This high-revving engine benefits from VarioCam Plus technology, delivering 320 hp through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is dialed in with Bilstein B8 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and rear-engine weight bias remain sharp. Key preventative maintenance is documented, including a LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recent rear main seal replacement. While the Arctic Silver paint and black leather interior show honest patina from spirited use, the car remains structurally sound with no bore scoring symptoms or fluid leaks. A perfect candidate for the enthusiast seeking peak analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
